## 渠道配置：飞书(Feishu)

我们的实例已配置了飞书渠道，通过以下设置：

```json
"channels": {
  "feishu": {
    "accounts": {
      "demo": {
        "enabled": true,
        "appId": "cli_a93d7b008ff6dcca",
        "appSecret": "XmzBxn0Snncsz8YK33aSNbqwhLrBeeEP",
        "connectionMode": "websocket",
        "domain": "feishu",
        "groupPolicy": "open"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

此配置将飞书消息路由到demo智能体，使用如下绑定规则：

```json
"bindings": [
  {
    "agentId": "demo",
    "match": {
      "channel": "feishu",
      "accountId": "demo"
    }
  }
]
```